{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/intellij/Intellij-setting-1","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"51636f39-2f3c-5141-a93c-a9bc81de479d","html":"<p>안녕하세요!</p>\n<p>개발 할 때 <code class=\"language-text\">Intellij</code>를 주로 사용 하는데 환경 설정 방법을 간혹 까먹는 경우가 있습니다.<br>\n그럴 때마다 매번 구글링 하기가 귀찮아서 이번 포스팅으로 환경 설정 방법을 정리 하고자 합니다.<br>\n(개발 환경을 <code class=\"language-text\">Mac OS</code>으로 사용하기 때문에 <code class=\"language-text\">Windows</code> 환경과 다를 수 있습니다!)</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"목차\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A9%EC%B0%A8\" aria-label=\"목차 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>목차</h1>\n<p><a href=\"#Font-&#x26;-Theme\">1. Font &#x26; Theme 설정 하기</a><br>\n<a href=\"#Github\">2. Github 설정 하기</a><br>\n<a href=\"#Tab-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">3. 창 여러개 Tab으로 띄우기</a><br>\n<a href=\"#%EB%8B%A8%EC%B6%95%ED%82%A4-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">4. 단축키 설정</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"font--theme\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#font--theme\" aria-label=\"font  theme permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Font &#x26; Theme</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Intellij에서 환경을 설정하는 방법 입니다. (<code class=\"language-text\">Mac</code>에서 설정하는 방법 입니다.)</li>\n<li>Intellij 폰트 설정</li>\n<li>글씨 폰트와 글씨 크기, 자간 등을 설정 할수 있습니다.</li>\n<li>메뉴: Preference > Appearance &#x26; Behavior > Appearance\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/8ecb0/intellij-font-setting.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/8ac56/intellij-font-setting.webp 240w,\n/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/d3be9/intellij-font-setting.webp 480w,\n/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/e46b2/intellij-font-setting.webp 960w,\n/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/655ae/intellij-font-setting.webp 989w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/8ff5a/intellij-font-setting.png 240w,\n/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/e85cb/intellij-font-setting.png 480w,\n/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/d9199/intellij-font-setting.png 960w,\n/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/8ecb0/intellij-font-setting.png 989w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/607a93a65855cf066de00d147282b09b/d9199/intellij-font-setting.png\"\n            alt=\"Font\"\n            title=\"Font\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>마우스 휠을 이용해서 폰트 크기를 조정</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Control+마우스 휠</code>을 이용해서 폰트 크기를 조정 할 수 있도록 하는 셋팅 입니다. 초기 셋에는 마우스 휠이 체크가 되어 있지 않으므로 설정 해주어야 합니다.</li>\n<li>메뉴: Preference > Editor > General\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/5caea/intellij-mouse-wheel.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/8ac56/intellij-mouse-wheel.webp 240w,\n/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/d3be9/intellij-mouse-wheel.webp 480w,\n/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/e46b2/intellij-mouse-wheel.webp 960w,\n/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/ef2bd/intellij-mouse-wheel.webp 996w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/8ff5a/intellij-mouse-wheel.png 240w,\n/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/e85cb/intellij-mouse-wheel.png 480w,\n/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/d9199/intellij-mouse-wheel.png 960w,\n/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/5caea/intellij-mouse-wheel.png 996w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a7cdd79c7e1b0b35bade7e156b60cd80/d9199/intellij-mouse-wheel.png\"\n            alt=\"Mouse wheel\"\n            title=\"Mouse wheel\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>Intellij 테마 설정</li>\n<li>Intellij 테마를 설정 할 수 있습니다. 저는 검정색의 <code class=\"language-text\">드라큘라</code> 테마 입니다.</li>\n<li>메뉴: Preference > Appearance &#x26; Behavior > Appearance\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/d1d24/intellij-theme-setting.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/8ac56/intellij-theme-setting.webp 240w,\n/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/d3be9/intellij-theme-setting.webp 480w,\n/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/e46b2/intellij-theme-setting.webp 960w,\n/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/b0d42/intellij-theme-setting.webp 987w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/8ff5a/intellij-theme-setting.png 240w,\n/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/e85cb/intellij-theme-setting.png 480w,\n/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/d9199/intellij-theme-setting.png 960w,\n/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/d1d24/intellij-theme-setting.png 987w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/bbb34359b96731d010bbf6199b790f95/d9199/intellij-theme-setting.png\"\n            alt=\"Appearance\"\n            title=\"Appearance\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"github\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#github\" aria-label=\"github permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Github</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Github 연동하기</li>\n<li>Intellij에서 Github와 연동하는 방법 입니다. 아래 <code class=\"language-text\">+</code> 버튼을 눌러서 자신의 깃허브 계정으로 로그인 합니다.  </li>\n<li>계정을 추가 하였으면 아래 <code class=\"language-text\">Apply</code> 버튼을 누르고 <code class=\"language-text\">OK</code> 버튼을 눌러서 저장 합니다.</li>\n<li>메뉴: Preference > Version Control > Github\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/5caea/intellij-github-setting.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.91666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/8ac56/intellij-github-setting.webp 240w,\n/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/d3be9/intellij-github-setting.webp 480w,\n/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/e46b2/intellij-github-setting.webp 960w,\n/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/ef2bd/intellij-github-setting.webp 996w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/8ff5a/intellij-github-setting.png 240w,\n/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/e85cb/intellij-github-setting.png 480w,\n/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/d9199/intellij-github-setting.png 960w,\n/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/5caea/intellij-github-setting.png 996w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ceaea9243758dd2d45b09da09c8f6266/d9199/intellij-github-setting.png\"\n            alt=\"Github\"\n            title=\"Github\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"tab-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tab-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"tab 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69